parameters:
Bunny-chan: As Memimi-chan's organization went through a
generational change, the veteran monsters who were managing
the Monster Fight also retired. As the head of the
management team, I'll make various reforms just like Memimi-
chan!

Memimi: You're so reliable, Bunny-chan. Thanks to all you've
done, Monster Fight is on the verge of a major leap forward
as a key industry. The dark organization will spare no
effort in providing personnel... Let's work hard together!

Memimi: ...By the way, lately Bunny-chan, you've been
spending time at the management headquarters without a
disguise... Is that okay? Showing your face could lead to
various...

Bunny-chan: It's fine, it's fine... Memimi-chan, you were
active without a disguise until recently, right? It wouldn't
be fair if only you were exposed. We're in this together♪

Bunny-chan: ...Well, our identities have been revealed for a
while now, and videos showing much more compromising stuff
than our faces are still spreading... It's better to just
embrace it and stand tall at this point...

Memimi: Together...! Let's keep pushing forward together,
Bunny-chan... You really are strong... sniff...

Anomalocaris Mosman: Mos mos mos... Did you see my match?
The crowd was going wild, right?

Memimi: You lost though, didn't you... Well, it's not like
the old betting matches or brawls, the excitement of the
crowd is what matters most...

Anomalocaris Mosman: You know it! Mos mos... Reigning at the
top of the merchandise sales is none other than my "Anomalo-
kun Acrylic Key Holder"! Don't you forget that!

Memimi: Why is something like this selling like crazy
nationwide through mail order... It's something to be
grateful for, but I just can't wrap my head around it...

Cerburus Octopus: Kekeke, I've become the number one
favorite among women this week!! The fight money isn't bad
either, this could be the start of my era! I might even get
a girlfriend...

Memimi: Ever since we made Monster Fight public, for some
reason, there are more female spectators... It's a
mystery... I don't really understand why guys like him and
Anomalocaris are so popular with women...

Cerburus Octopus: Women, they like to see men tangled up
with each other!! I'm sure of it because I accidentally
bought a manga like that at the bookstore once...
Memimi: Is that so...? I don't really get it...

Minion: There are many minions in the underworld who only
know how to fight, but thanks to the great boss and Bunny-
chan's excellent management of personnel, everyone has been
able to earn money in matches and find jobs that suit
them... I'm grateful.

Memimi: Our ultimate goal is to create a society where
everyone can live in peace, regardless of whether it's
aboveground or underground. We want to help those who have
once dropped out to be able to try again.

Minion: You're an amazing person... I'm starting to feel
slightly guilty about the times we all gangbanged you or
made you spread your pussy in front of the station for
everyone to photograph...

Memimi: I do want you to feel very guilty about it... The
damage I suffered from that incident... I don't even want to
remember it...

Monster: The cleaning of the venue is perfect! Ever since we
started letting in the general public, we've been very
careful about hygiene. Dynamite Abalone, who has become part
of the management team, is also working hard.

Memimi: Indeed, Monster Fight has now become entertainment
watched by people all over the world through live streaming.
We can't afford to show anything unsightly... it would drive
away the viewers that we've worked so hard to increase!

Monster: Well, the reason for the increase in viewers is due
to the videos of Lord Shark Duke being massively reposted...
They streamed him being gangbanged uncensored for hours on
end... It inadvertently became our best promotion...

Memimi: Quiet... there's no need to say it out loud... Even
if we delete them, they're just re-uploaded immediately, and
frustratingly, we're actually benefiting from it, so we have
no choice but to leave it be... ugh...

Monster: Sorry... Oh, but it's not just Lord Shark Duke's
videos that are bringing in viewers! Bunny-chan's videos are
also being spread all over... She was already famous for her
violin, so the noise about her on the net is quite
something...

Bunny-chan: You don't have to talk about that... It became a
serious issue, but the mayor and others took action, and I
was spared from being expelled... It's still hard to get
used to the stares from people around me though...

Bunny-chan: When I'm feeling down, nothing beats the
electric remote control! I'm going to make full use of this
thing until I get tired of it! I have to stay cheerful all
the time, or I won't be able to do my job as the Monster
Fight referee♪

Memimi: Bunny-chan is really strong... Somehow, it makes me
feel energized too...

Dynamite Abalone: Oh, when I receive Bunny-chan's electric
shocks, I somehow feel energized... Being a jack-of-all-
trades for Monster Fight might just be my calling... huff
huff... I have to work hard today too, so I can get plenty
of electricity flowing...
Memimi: This guy is tough too...
